Calling all Ladies of Saigon and beyond!! 
Island Touch is finaly touching Vietnam!!
Dont miss the chance to become a part of the largest Bachata family in the World!

 When you are a member of a Touch Team, you will..
 * Receive training in Island Touch Bachata style and technique
 * Learn choreography by world-renowned Jorge Burgos & Tanja Kensinger (Ataca & La Alemana)
 * Perform at various socials and events
 * Have an opportunity to share the stage with Touch Teams from around the globe at national/international congresses & festivals
 * Gain confidence in your social dancing
 * Make memories that will last a lifetime and friends that become family

 No registration fee

 Please arrive 10 minutes earlier to allow registration and warm up.